## 25 February 2026 (Weekend Mini Project)

### Project: Simple Form with Database

### Features

* User input form
* Data database mein store

### Code

```php id="php08"
<?php
$conn = mysqli_connect("localhost", "root", "", "test");

if ($_SERVER["REQUEST_METHOD"] == "POST") {
    $name = $_POST['name'];

    $sql = "INSERT INTO users (name) VALUES ('$name')";
    mysqli_query($conn, $sql);
}
?>

<form method="POST">
  <input type="text" name="name">
  <button type="submit">Submit</button>
</form>
```

### Learning Outcome

* Frontend + Backend + Database connect kiya
* Real application ka basic flow samajh aaya

### Improvement Areas

* Security (SQL injection prevention)
